Priority: extra
Maintainer: Percona Development <mysql-dev@percona.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.3), libaio-dev, wget, automake,
 libtool, bison, libncurses-dev, libz-dev, libssl-dev, cmake, bzr, ca-certificates
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
